Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 26.02.25
Welcome to GunzX (“we,” “our,” or “us”). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you visit our apps and website.
1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information, but only with your explicit consent:
Personal Information
: Such as your name, email address, and any other information you provide voluntarily (e.g., when signing up for a newsletter or contacting us). We do not collect personal data without your consent.
Non-Personal Information
: Such as browser type, IP address, and usage data collected automatically through cookies and analytics tools.
2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect to:
Provide and maintain our website
Improve user experience
Respond to inquiries and customer service requests
Send newsletters or marketing communications (if opted in)
Monitor and analyze website performance
3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
We may use cookies and similar technologies to collect data about your browsing behavior. You can adjust your browser settings to refuse cookies; however, this may impact website functionality.
4. Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services (e.g., analytics, advertising, or payment processors) that collect, use, and share data according to their privacy policies. We are not responsible for their practices.
5. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
6. Your Rights
Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at contact@gunzx.com.
7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: contact@gunzx.com
By using our website, you consent to this Privacy Policy.